mic tone mapping,custom pro panel,亮度會比其它oled高<br />\nP記GZ1500: 配套同功能上同GZ2000差唔多，差別在於個音響step down<br />\nP記GZ1000：配套同功能上同GZ1500差唔多，只係影像處理器同音響再step down<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nLG C9:有dv有earc,有airplay 2,4個port 都係hdmi 2.1,<span style=\"font-size: small;\">會有g sync update？（need fc）</span>,有dynamic tone mapping<br />\n<br />\nLG B9:配套同功能上同c9大致相同，只係影像處理器step down<br />\n<br />\nlast post: <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1637887/\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1637887/</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"76924194ad8ce5aa7c827f80eabb031d0a9f348b","tid":1748485,"uid":321891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:31:34.000Z","msg":"一入~"},{"pid":"b5ec517a8a46a0fe671ccbcb658ab1fa011f5193","tid":1748485,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T05:10:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位巴打記住投票<br />\n齊齊踢走保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"e54120b2b69eaade52d9ca4bd9c8c219a4b3e427","tid":1748485,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T05:31:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位巴打記住投票<br />\n齊齊踢走保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"6c0c939894c37a9842957dff34a484f7e5de6fb6","tid":1748485,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T05:32:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位巴打記住投票<br />\n齊齊踢走保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"bab57ac22f9ba9895e5b7bb0a9bb337f24b13ff1","tid":1748485,"uid":2474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T06:19:39.000Z","msg":"各位巴打記住投票<br />\n齊齊踢走保皇黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif